        Energy Efficiency and NatHERS Ratings: How Energy Performance Affects Brisbane Property Buyers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Energy efficiency is moving from a fringe concern to a meaningful buyer signal in Brisbane. Here is what NatHERS measures, when ratings apply, what sellers can do at low cost, and what to disclose.
      </p>
